methods.getChart:
Gets the Chart at the specified location in this array.

:param row: (int) - row of the Chart
:param col: (int) - column of the Chart
:return: (io.deephaven.plot.ChartImpl) the Chart at the specified location in this array.
methods.getCharts:
Gets the Charts in this ChartArray.

:return: (java.util.List<io.deephaven.plot.ChartImpl>) list of Charts in this ChartArray
methods.getIndex:
Gets the index of the Chart at the specified location in this array.

:param row: (int) - row of the Chart
:param col: (int) - column of the Chart
:return: (int) index of the Chart at the specified location in this array.
methods.isEmpty:
Whether the index indicates that there is no Chart in that location.

:param index: (int) - index of the Chart
:return: (boolean) Whether the index indicates that there is no Chart in that location
